  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1005">
<l>koṭuppatūun tuyppatūu millārk kaṭukkiya </l>
<l>kōṭiyuṇ ṭāyiṉu mil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who neither give (to others) nor enjoy (their property) are (truly) destitute, though possessing immense riches.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
